ComicInfo.Summary:
Angel takes control of the very undead Centurions that were hunting her. However, as she begins to build her own army and carve out her own stake across the European continent, the new Zombie Tramp quickly discovers that the only thing worse than trying to survive a horde of ancient Roman zombies… is trying to control them for her own bidding!
Features 3 regular and risqué variants, including the special Bryan Baugh variants!!!
